song_name: Cant Keep A Good Band Down

version_description: Simple rhythm guitar interpretation from the song https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2yr716tmF4A.
This one includes the nuances that the other 'basic' chord version doesn't.
A gem from the Demon's and Wizards album. I have yet to see this properly done anywhere.
This is an easy version, suitable for beginners. Just four basic chords - C, D, G, Am. Sounds fine acoustic.
Intro was keyboard heavy on 1973 vinyl release. Original can be heard on youtube.
